description:
H5: src/components/ui/chart.tsx
```tsx
export function ChartTooltip({ children }: ChartTooltipProps) {
  return <>{children}</>
}
export function ChartLegend({ children }: ChartLegendProps) {
  return <>{children}</>
}
```
These provide no functionality. The container/Content split is non-functional — ChartTooltipContent and ChartLegendContent are pure-presentational with no recharts hook integration. Consumers must wire recharts tooltip/legend manually. These components are misleading — they look like they provide integration but don't.
